To run this test against other shells, use the shell argument, eg:
run-tests.py --shell=zsh test-scm-prompt*

  $ configure mutation-norecord

Initialize scm prompt
  $ . $TESTDIR/../contrib/scm-prompt.sh

  $ cmd() {
  >   "$@"
  >   _scm_prompt "(%s)\n"
  > }

